short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Help sync your contacts and connections data for Graphlan

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
The official Graphlan contacts / connections extension!  

Add how you met and notes to connections from across the web, and organize them into lists as well.

If you have a Graphlan account, get the most out of it by installing this extension and synchronizing data from across the web.
